Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终的舞台在呼唤我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----------------新OP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.19,0:00:37.75,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:44.95,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反転する世界のプラトニック 愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:01:00.60,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僕らが見てる世界は いつでも逆さまで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.42,0:01:11.07,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どうしようもないことで たいがい決まってく
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:23.15,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涙するほど傷つく瞳 心で叫びながら黙っていた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:33.74,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後のふたり 混ざれないまま 秒読みが聞こえてくる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:01:39.90,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絶望的に君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:45.75,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,すたれゆく動物みたいに愛し合おう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:50.12,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泣きたいくらい君はきれいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:53.46,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反転する世界のプラトニック
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:56.47,opj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感じたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.19,0:00:37.75,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你美得令人绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.90,0:00:44.95,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们在倒错的精神世界中相爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.19,0:01:00.60,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们眼里的世界总是相互颠倒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.42,0:01:11.07,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这几乎要被认定为是无可奈何的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.47,0:01:23.15,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤口淌泪的眼眸 在内心沉默地叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:33.74,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后的两人来不及结合便听到离别的倒数
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:01:39.90,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你美得令人绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.16,0:01:45.75,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们像渐趋衰老的动物一样相爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:50.12,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你美得令人落泪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:53.46,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在倒错的精神世界里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:56.47,opc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想细细体会…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,==================OP=================
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.36,0:02:08.90,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\pos(719,400)}复活之翼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.67,0:02:15.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这音色 这旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.55,0:02:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太适合于最终乐章了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.47,0:02:22.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续吧 继续奏响吧 Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.15,0:02:27.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身体哪里还藏有如此强大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.32,0:02:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优雅而纤细
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但又灼热而激烈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:34.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,气势雄浑地响彻心底
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.78,0:02:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特在不穿Element制服的情况下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过强行露出自己的肌肤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使自己的感官得到进一步的加强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但肉体所受的打击应该相当巨大
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.75,0:02:51.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那简直就是舍身战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为我的灵魂奉上最精彩的独奏协奏曲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(577,440)\fs24}Kadenz
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候我所看到的不是幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.97,0:03:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪第一次相遇时没有闻到你的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.91,0:03:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你和我有着相同的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.38,0:03:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这张照片里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.62,0:03:22.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时也是你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我原本是一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 直到那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:38.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:04.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天 那个只能任由命运摆布的阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:07.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.19,0:04:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到现在你也没什么改变
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是那个一到关键时刻就束手无策的胆小鬼阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.23,0:04:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又有什么了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到最后都救不了妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去Altair都做些什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:32.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然穿越了次元 但我和母亲失散了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:35.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候我遇到了未影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎 半身的你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.07,0:04:41.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗之阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫做神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起你就叫神乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去了记忆 由未影一手抚养
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.54,0:05:04.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 母亲的事已经无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.75,0:05:08.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跟连不明来历的父亲也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说重要的气味是唯一的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.99,0:05:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有心爱的臭女人的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的希尔菲而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.05,0:05:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是胆小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会把御子乃交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真弱真弱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 为什么你们两人要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.28,0:05:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳之翼终于觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:25.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看你是怎么地不软弱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:37.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.53,0:06:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希尔菲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.19,0:06:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.50,0:07:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.93,0:07:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高次元量子反应
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在湖泊一带的地底下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个标志是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:36.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion居然产生了共鸣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是从1万2千年前的太古传来的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:44.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:49.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那正是传说中的神话型Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳之翼终于现身了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.42,0:08:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.03,0:08:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:26.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希尔菲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好想你啊 希尔菲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跨越了1万2千年的时空
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在终于能够杀死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.29,0:08:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要杀掉御子乃?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.15,0:08:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 我要杀掉她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.19,0:08:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦地 激烈地 冷酷地 无数次地杀死她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.31,0:08:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要杀掉你 阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:08:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着我 希尔菲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.53,0:09:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉他之后 让我们好好地厮杀至天明
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.47,0:09:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你碰她一根指头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.56,0:09:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高次元量子等级正持续上升
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.78,0:09:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会错的 这是真家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.30,0:09:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神话型Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.95,0:09:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说终于化为现实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:38.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们正身处在如此伟大的历史瞬间面前吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.15,0:09:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 明明到了这么重要的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙到底在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.14,0:09:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是传说之一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.76,0:09:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不动总司令 您什么时候回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打情骂俏 犬亦不理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:03.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.44,0:10:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝不交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放弃吧 这是1万2千年前就已经决定好的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和希尔菲结合的不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论你怎么挣扎也无法战胜命运
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.38,0:10:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和希尔菲正因是被命运所指引着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.05,0:10:34.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以即使身处不同的星球也能相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.18,0:10:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有着能跨越命运的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有翅膀 不用以飞翔也是毫无意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能飞起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 飞起来给我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.80,0:10:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 你不可以继续伤害阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.78,0:10:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的笑脸太难看了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.43,0:10:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我越来越想杀死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.81,0:11:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑吧 继续笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.74,0:11:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续吧 继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.77,0:11:20.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经死了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.31,0:11:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 你没事啊 婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿马塔才是 难道说你是担心我才回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婕希卡 我终于意识到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:46.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正重要的到底是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.07,0:11:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:11:59.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.37,0:12:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我的约定还没有兑现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.71,0:12:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还不能死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 你和我的约定还没有兑现
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再看到你们两人互相伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.47,0:12:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.08,0:12:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天一定要做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.77,0:12:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要了断什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.17,0:12:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是因为命运才追求御子乃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.63,0:12:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 不要让我一再说明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.78,0:12:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.72,0:13:02.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管御子乃是不是希尔菲转世
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.86,0:13:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和1万2千年前的命运也没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.70,0:13:10.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对现在的…现在的御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:12.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.92,0:13:14.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.42,0:13:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在 此时此刻 这一瞬间的 御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就在这里较量一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.79,0:13:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的命运和你的痴情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.56,0:13:29.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪个更加强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:40.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.12,0:13:51.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳之翼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:02.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会输个你这种人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.94,0:14:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一点 还差一点我所追求的旋律就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.63,0:14:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.63,0:14:16.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.72,0:14:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你怎么了 修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听得到吗 挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这音色很美妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.78,0:14:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希尔菲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特的生命等级异常低下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.23,0:14:49.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续进行战斗会危及性命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更换Element
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由柚叶替换修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.04,0:14:54.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.08,0:14:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还能战斗 还差一步
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.44,0:15:02.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差一步 我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.32,0:15:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更换Element 快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.71,0:15:10.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚叶·苏尔 参战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里逃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.03,0:15:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神话型Aquarion的高次元量子反应已经超出了检测范围
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:35.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不动 你到底想要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.49,0:15:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切不都已经显示在创圣之书上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神话只能由高尚的生命撰写
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:48.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 以流荡着的血液为墨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有阻止的意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻止还是怂恿都是一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.57,0:16:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合十的双手之间到底有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中什么也没有 只有无
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.87,0:16:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 无虽无 但又不尽为无
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正负的两种力量相互抵消产生出无的形态
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.30,0:16:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃·铃白的连接之力亦然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.55,0:16:28.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光与暗 圣与邪 善与恶 还有阴与阳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人封闭着的记忆被打开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.52,0:16:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从虚无中诞生的无限力量开始运动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.04,0:16:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是现在新的一页即将翻开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.95,0:17:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.50,0:17:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳之翼在我的怀抱中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.10,0:17:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神话型Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:49.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.88,0:17:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门打开了 我们也快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:13.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2台Abductor以及神话型Aquarion冲入了次元之门中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 克蕾亚理事长
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请再一次 再一次让我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:29.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次真的会没命哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你收留的我来到Neo DEAVA时就已经明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:41.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一天迟早会到来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:03.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请答应我一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曲子完成以后也让我听一听
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.17,0:19:18.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.81,0:19:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.78,0:19:27.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2台Vector闯入次元之门
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.09,0:19:29.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监视器画面被中断
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:37.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御子乃和神乐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:46.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在奏响最后的乐曲之前
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先夺回神话型Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.01,0:19:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是只有两人的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.74,0:19:54.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来跟你们合体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.78,0:19:56.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婕希卡 你没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:20:01.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿马塔 这就是我的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:06.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命运合体 GO Aquarion
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:16.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿马塔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.93,0:20:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 婕希卡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.18,0:20:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵魂在颤动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.75,0:20:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion SPADA
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.83,0:20:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神话型被…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:40.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磔刑斩击剑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.88,0:20:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\pos(424,439)}CRUCIFXION SWORD
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.37,0:21:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次元之门开启
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.98,0:21:23.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mithra Gnis入侵我领域
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.79,0:21:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,机体中有Rare·Igler反应
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让神乐如此执着的Rare·Igler
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.90,0:21:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的一定是真实的夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备出击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能让神乐独占真实的夏娃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.69,0:21:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从世界各地传来地壳变动和气候异常的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于解除了神话型Aquarion的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.95,0:22:00.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Altair和Vega之间保持至今的平衡已经被打破
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.95,0:22:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神话型Aquarion被夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.24,0:22:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和修雷特他们的通信也依然断绝着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.27,0:22:09.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这边就没有什么办法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.91,0:22:12.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界将会怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.76,0:22:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在放弃还太早
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.53,0:22:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳之翼只有被选中的Element才能操纵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.69,0:22:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时机终于来临了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.13,0:22:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到你履行约定的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.56,0:22:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草绿色头发的你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.36,0:24:24.78,biaoti,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\pos(271,400)}神话旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.00,0:24:13.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我告诉你我喜欢的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.97,0:24:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点点的花瓣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.62,0:24:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神乐的咆哮
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.73,0:24:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌的东西也告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.22,0:24:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是欺骗 背叛 和那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===================ED=====================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.57,0:22:58.34,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}君へ続く坂道に 白い花が咲いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.48,0:23:06.15,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}夢から覚めたあとも 悲しい空見てた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.64,0:23:16.13,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}この気持ち葉っぱの裏に住んでる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.99,0:23:25.63,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}朝露が落ちる音に 耳をすませてるの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:33.49,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}神様 あなたが造った世界は 完璧じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:41.08,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}ここでは毎日恋がポロポロ 死んでゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.28,0:23:45.27,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}はじめて好きになったの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:48.43,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}あなたは知らないでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.56,0:23:52.96,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}地球の裏側でいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.14,0:23:56.17,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}そばにいてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.36,0:24:00.50,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}私を忘れてもいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.72,0:24:07.01,nedj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}そばにいてほしかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.57,0:22:58.34,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}延伸到你身旁的坡道 点缀着雪白的花朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.48,0:23:06.15,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}从睡梦中惊醒之后 远望着忧伤的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.64,0:23:16.13,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}这份青涩的感觉 依存在绿叶错综的纹路之间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.99,0:23:25.63,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}侧耳聆听 晨露缓缓落下的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.82,0:23:33.49,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}神明您所创造的这个世界并不完美
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:41.08,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}因为这里每天都有恋情一段接一段地告终
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.28,0:23:45.27,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我是初尝恋爱的滋味
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:48.43,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}这个你应该不知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.56,0:23:52.96,jedc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}即便永不见天日也没关系
